  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project supports vulnerable rural and urban communities, especially women, in Indonesia by increasing climate resilient sustainable livelihoods, preparedness response and adaptive capacity to disasters, and enabling inclusive disaster risk management systems.&#xA0; The project aims to ensure vulnerable households have climate resilient and sustainable livelihoods, and can&#xA0;cope with climate change impacts.&#xA0; The project also aims to ensure communities have disaster risk management systems and practices that are inclusive of women and people with disabilities.</narrative>
